//     with the v2 bounded rule set. Returns post-tokenization byte count.
//
//   PASS 3 — selftest fixtures (5 + 3 latency probes)
//     F1: byte-eq mixed-JSON (raw 142 D2 try-revert below MIN_BYTES — small
//          fixture forces identity passthrough; verifies pre-gate honored).
//     F2: byte-eq Korean multibyte (raw 137 byte-faithful round-trip).
//     F3: byte-eq large-text 4KB-32KB (forces real bounded-n-gram path).
//     F4: PCFG escape unit (rule_marker 254 / escape 255 escape-unit test).
//     F5: bits/byte sanity floor on 4KB English (estimator does NOT fabricate
//          sub-1.0 bit/byte on small samples, raw 91 honest C3).
